label: High to Low
short_description: Resistance moves from above the head diagonally down toward the waist.

label: High to Mid
short_description: Resistance moves from above the head diagonally down toward the chest.

label: High to High
short_description: Resistance moves horizontally at head height.

label: Mid to High
short_description: Resistance moves from chest height diagonally up toward the face.

label: Mid to Mid
short_description: Resistance moves horizontally at chest height.

label: Mid to Low

label: Low to High
short_description: Resistance moves from the floor diagonally up toward the face.

label: Low to Mid
short_description: Resistance moves from the floor diagonally up toward the chest.

label: Low to Low
short_description: Resistance moves horizontally at hip/waist height.
